[cheering]

13:45.032 --> 13:47.201
Let's make Earth great again!

13:47.284 --> 13:48.160
Say it with me!

13:48.244 --> 13:51.121
Let's make Earth great again!

13:51.205 --> 13:52.498
Cue fire.

13:53.874 --> 13:55.709
[all] Ooh...

13:57.586 --> 13:59.129
Citizens of Earth,

13:59.213 --> 14:03.801
welcome to Max's Farmapalooza.

14:03.884 --> 14:05.678
[cheering]

14:07.972 --> 14:10.474
Who thinks fruits and vegetables
are good for you?

14:11.684 --> 14:15.312
Well, they're even better for you
when they're grown organically,

14:15.396 --> 14:17.231
with no pesticides.

14:17.314 --> 14:18.482
[pantomime baddie music]

14:20.109 --> 14:22.236
Boo, pesticides!

14:22.319 --> 14:24.196
[all] Boo!

14:24.822 --> 14:26.407
Yay, organic!

14:26.490 --> 14:27.825
[all] Yay!

14:28.951 --> 14:31.120
[clapping and cheering]

14:33.539 --> 14:34.582
[Jimmy] OK, Steph.

14:35.416 --> 14:36.333
It's been 12 hours.

14:36.417 --> 14:39.920
Are you ready to see how many millions
of hits our "Boy Next Door" video has?

14:40.546 --> 14:43.799
I'm sure it doesn't have millions.
Maybe tens of thousands.

14:45.718 --> 14:47.428
OK, well, here we go.

14:47.845 --> 14:48.971
And...

14:50.306 --> 14:52.182
41 views?

14:52.725 --> 14:54.852
37 thumbs down?

14:56.854 --> 14:59.440
And all of the comments
say that we're annoying.

14:59.523 --> 15:04.236
No, not this one. This one says,
"You need a haircut, you dirty hippie."

15:06.071 --> 15:07.323
"And so does he!"?

15:11.535 --> 15:13.787
Kimmy, come look at our video.
Are we annoying?

